[
  {
    "text": "So, what brings\nyou two to Akumal?",
    "start": 1.084,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Vacation\nfrom the kids?",
    "start": 3.586,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, no kids.",
    "start": 5.046,
    "duration": 0.751
  },
  {
    "text": "That ship has sailed.",
    "start": 5.797,
    "duration": 0.792
  },
  {
    "text": "It's our ten year\nanniversary.",
    "start": 7.09,
    "duration": 1.668
  },
  {
    "text": "Take these, as they\nwill get you",
    "start": 8.758,
    "duration": 2.503
  },
  {
    "text": "everything you need.",
    "start": 11.261,
    "duration": 0.876
  },
  {
    "text": "Even heroin?",
    "start": 12.47,
    "duration": 0.709
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry?",
    "start": 13.179,
    "duration": 0.584
  },
  {
    "text": "She's joking.",
    "start": 13.763,
    "duration": 0.709
  },
  {
    "text": "That was a bad joke.",
    "start": 14.472,
    "duration": 0.793
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm starting to\nforget who I am.",
    "start": 15.598,
    "duration": 2.378
  },
  {
    "text": "No work, no stress,\nno regrets.",
    "start": 18.351,
    "duration": 3.671
  },
  {
    "text": "Why don't we just see\nwhere this leads us?",
    "start": 22.564,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "This phone belonged\nto a kid who went",
    "start": 36.369,
    "duration": 1.627
  },
  {
    "text": "missing down here\nfifteen years ago.",
    "start": 37.996,
    "duration": 1.585
  },
  {
    "text": "It belonged to\nSam Lawford.",
    "start": 42.876,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "Sam, and his mom,\nand his dad",
    "start": 46.129,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "and his girlfriend arrived\nat this resort",
    "start": 47.63,
    "duration": 1.419
  },
  {
    "text": "on Christmas night.",
    "start": 49.049,
    "duration": 0.667
  },
  {
    "text": "But then, the\nnext morning,",
    "start": 50.884,
    "duration": 1.543
  },
  {
    "text": "he's gone.",
    "start": 52.427,
    "duration": 0.751
  },
  {
    "text": "Later on, this other\nguest from the resort",
    "start": 55.346,
    "duration": 1.502
  },
  {
    "text": "was also\nreported missing.",
    "start": 57.265,
    "duration": 1.835
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you want to\nget out of here?",
    "start": 60.977,
    "duration": 1.251
  },
  {
    "text": "My daughter wanted\nto spend Christmas here.",
    "start": 62.771,
    "duration": 2.168
  },
  {
    "text": "But she didn't want\nto spend it with me.",
    "start": 65.648,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "We found the\nboy's skateboard.",
    "start": 71.154,
    "duration": 2.002
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you ever feel like something from the past",
    "start": 76.493,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "is missing from your future?",
    "start": 78.119,
    "duration": 1.377
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm gonna get\nsome answers.",
    "start": 82.207,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, come back here!",
    "start": 84.751,
    "duration": 1.501
  },
  {
    "text": "But what if there\naren't any answers?",
    "start": 87.754,
    "duration": 1.626
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, there have to be,",
    "start": 93.426,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "because otherwise what\nis the fucking point?",
    "start": 95.136,
    "duration": 1.877
  }
]